            "type": "section",
            "title": "Instructions",
            "content": {
                "type": "steps",
                "items": [
                    "Begin by sitting on a sturdy chair with your back straight and your feet flat on the ground.",
                    "Place your hands on the sides of the chair for support.",
                    "Slowly lift one leg off the ground, keeping it straight and extended in front of you.",
                    "Hold the position for a few seconds, then lower your leg back down to the starting position.",
                    "Repeat the exercise with the other leg.",
                    "Continue alternating legs for the desired number of repetitions."
                ]
            }
        },
